{"tid":1285142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"讓我待你好一點","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:03:26.000Z","uid":270468,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ef00c13b1c0905e0358b716d355c4c3bf40ea8","tid":1285142,"uid":270468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1r1yuDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1r1yuDU.jpg&h=3df42fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢副唔可以叫做畫、<br />\n但這樣亂點一通嘅顔色、<br />\n就好似大家嘅人生一樣、<br />\n由一張白紙開始、<br />\n逐點逐點經歷加上去.<br />\n可以好齊整、亦可以不規則、<br />\n但每一次嘅作品都無可能一樣、<br />\n就如我們不可能被 複製<br />\n當中會有一些黑點、<br />\n但只要唔好用放大鏡去聚焦<br />\n放眼看呢副畫、 仍然係色彩斑斕<br />\n我哋有追求自由嘅生活權利<br />\n我哋亦都有能力去選擇我哋嘅視線<br />\n黑點正正襯托起其他顏色更鮮豔<br />\n以前我好鍾意聽呢首歌<br />\n讓我待你好一點<br />\n係因為有兩句歌詞好舒服<br />\n沒有酸那覺甜<br />\n沒有風怎知暖"},{"pid":"ab55b0234214f8d00743c6dc475c91704fda031a","tid":1285142,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93b83bce2713ba3e9bef7e0ed52e17fcf589378","tid":1285142,"uid":270468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"勞煩入嚟屌下我"},{"pid":"967bf0e738731760df9f60fcb2e959ea36da9263","tid":1285142,"uid":270468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab55b0234214f8d00743c6dc475c91704fda031a","tid":1285142,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"7月7日晚、啱啱响大6坐高鐵返、希望趕得切嚟加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36abf2f31cb45da18faa53